data.description: At Santa Rosa Highlands, there's a home that's just your style. You'll find everything you desire amidst the natural grandeur of rolling hills set against the majestic backdrop of the Cleveland National Forest. It's gracious country living with the excitement of the city just minutes away. Life is more than a house, which is why Santa Rosa Highlands offers a wide array of thoughtfully designed community amenities for residents of all ages. If it's fun, it happens here. The community Recreation Center features a Clubhouse, covered patio, warming Kitchen, pools, outdoor showers, and BBQ's. Playtime is steps from home at our on-site park which features a tot-lot, turn play areas, pet stations, and inviting benches along winding paseos. Come Reach Greater Heights at Santa Rosa Highlands!
